{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775859990781,"sessionID":"ses_286835f93ffelyzrAay21blODp","part":{"id":"prt_d7980fca0001XmcIqxhiPswDR3","messageID":"msg_d7980dce80017xH1f6HLIVUeTm","sessionID":"ses_286835f93ffelyzrAay21blODp","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_functions.read:14","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-010/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-010/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-010: Router 会话管理 - Design Document\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: _TBD: High-level design description for session management in the router._\n6: \n7: ## Goals\n8: \n9: - _TBD: Session creation and initialization_\n10: - _TBD: Session state tracking_\n11: - _TBD: Session affinity routing_\n12: - _TBD: Session lifecycle management_\n13: \n14: ## Architecture\n15: \n16: _TBD: Component diagrams and architecture decisions_\n17: \n18: ## Data Models\n19: \n20: _TBD: Session data structures and schemas_\n21: \n22: ## API Design\n23: \n24: _TBD: Public interfaces and APIs_\n25: \n26: ## Implementation Notes\n27: \n28: _TBD: Key implementation considerations_\n29: \n30: ## References\n31: \n32: - AR-009: Router HTTP 反向代理核心\n\n(End of file - total 32 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-010: Router 会话管理 - Design Document\n\n## Overview\n\n_TBD: High-level design description for session management in the router._\n\n## Goals\n\n- _TBD: Session creation and initialization_\n- _TBD: Session state tracking_\n- _TBD: Session affinity routing_\n- _TBD: Session lifecycle management_\n\n## Architecture\n\n_TBD: Component diagrams and architecture decisions_\n\n## Data Models\n\n_TBD: Session data structures and schemas_","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/chan